---
description: Testing and code quality guidelines
globs:
alwaysApply: agent
---

- Ensure lint, test, and build pass before committing.
- Use PHPUnit + Orchestra Testbench for unit/component/integration tests.
- E2E browser tests are not part of the default package workflow.
- Place tests alongside implementation files or in `tests/` directory.
- Aim for meaningful test coverage of business logic.
